# Project: ESTI MCP Router

Use the chain:

```text
Locate → Understand → Edit → Verify → Store lesson if needed
```

Do not start with global Grep/Glob if MCP/index tools are available.

## Device profile

Read `DEVICE_PROFILE` / `MCP_PROFILE` from `.dev.env`.

### POWER profile

| Phase | Primary | Fallback |
|---|---|---|
| Locate BSL/procedure | `bsl-atlas-esti` `search_function` / `codesearch` | `code-index` |
| Locate metadata | `bsl-atlas-esti` `metadatasearch` | `litecode browse/object_structure` |
| Semantic search | `codesearch` | `metadatasearch` + targeted grep |
| Roles/access | `litecode.get_access` | metadata search |
| Callers/impact | `lean-ctx.ctx_callgraph` / `ctx_impact` | Serena references |
| Edit | Serena after locate | native edit |
| Verify | naparnik + v8std | manual checklist |
| Live infobase | `mcp-1c` | `1c-rest-mcp` |

### LITE profile

| Phase | Primary | Fallback |
|---|---|---|
| Locate | `litecode.search_metadata` / `get_routines` | `code-index.grep_body` |
| Semantic search | `litecode.search_by_embedding` | `find_routines_by_description` |
| Metadata graph | `litecode.get_references` / `object_structure` | `get_data_links` |
| Roles/access | `litecode.get_access` | targeted metadata read |
| Edit | Serena after locate | native edit |
| Verify | naparnik + v8std | manual checklist |

Do not call heavy `bsl-atlas-esti` on LITE if `.dev.env` says it is disabled.

## Locate rules

| Intent | First action |
|---|---|
| Known procedure name | search exact function/routine |
| Unknown meaning | semantic search by business phrase |
| Metadata object | metadata search/browse/object_structure |
| Role/access | `get_access` before grep |
| Public API change | callers/impact before edit |
| CFE patch | locate original method/procedure + extension analogue |

## Anti-patterns

- Serena `find_symbol` across whole configuration before locate.
- Calling Atlas + litecode + code-index for the same simple query.
- Using grep for role rights when `get_access` exists.
- Editing by file name guess without confirming metadata object.
- Running verification before saving the changed target.
